<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.4">
<l>karumavaṉ pācaṅ kaḻittuḻaṉ ṟuyyavē</l>
<l>perumalai yeṭuttāṉ pīṭuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>varumaḻai tavaḻu māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>tirumalai yatuvē yaṭaivatu tiṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For escaping with effort after removing the strong sling of karma</l>
<l>that way reaching that, [namely] the sacred mountain</l>
<l>of Māliruñcōlai where the coming clouds creep up</l>
<l>to the temple where dwells the might of him who lifted the big mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
